  6:{title:"Love, Responsibility & Service",theme:"The great themes are love, home, family, and responsibility. Life places others in your care — and in caring for them, you discover dimensions of yourself you had not yet met.",love:"The most significant relationship events of your life may occur now — marriage, deep commitment, or healing of family patterns.",career:"Healing, counselling, teaching, design, and community service align with this phase.",inner:"Learn where responsibility ends and martyrdom begins.",advice:"Tend your own garden first. From abundance within, you can give to others endlessly."},
